<%= govuk_panel(title_text: "#{@wizard.school.induction_tutor_name} is your school’s induction tutor") %>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What happens next</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">We’ll send an email to <%= @wizard.school.induction_tutor_name %> at <%= @wizard.school.induction_tutor_email %> to let them know.</p>
<p class="govuk-body">We’ll also let your school’s appropriate body and lead providers know about the change. <%= @wizard.school.induction_tutor_name %> will be their main contact for early career training and induction at your school.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">
  <%= govuk_button_link_to("Continue", schools_ects_home_path) %>
</p>
